<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>第九次监测合格农业产业化</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>国家重点龙头企业名单</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">（湖南名单）</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201216/6949927ae7e44b00aa9c2269bc329e1b.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
